review: It was really a wonderful experience at Dr Tarun's Dental.Few days back i reported in the clinic with severe pain in my tooth ,I could easily locate this clinic because of its online presence on Practo .I was really impressed by the way I was greeted by the staff and doctors who made comfortable to come out of my fear and anxiety as it was my first dental visit ,I was thoroughly explained about my treatment plan regarding painless single sitting root canal treatment and 2 implants placement to replace my 2 of my lower missing teeth and all the procedures were completed well on time.So i will definitely recommend this clinic to all for any kind of dental problem.
He is an intermediary humble person with true expertise n skills. I have visited his clinic twice with true satisfaction.

Good Service and work is appreciated and customers satisfied. 
Doctor behavior is good and communication is also good.
Clinic cleanness is good and clinic hygiene is also maintain.
Excellent service with neat and clean clinic. I would recommend Dr. Tarun to all my colleague for all their dental treatment.
